c: 42
v: 7
t: "Kuma kamar haka ne Muka yi wahayin abin karãntãwa (Alƙur'ãni) na Lãrabci zuwa gare ka, dõmin ka yi gargaɗi ga Uwar Alƙaryu (Makka) da wanda ke a kẽwayenta, kuma ka yi gargaɗi game da rãnar taruwa, bãbu shakka gare ta, wata ƙungiya tanã a cikin Aljanna kuma wata ƙungiya tãna a cikin sa'ĩr"